-case-dismissed-3374849">Smithline 提起的诉讼已被驳回</a>，而曼森<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-says-assault-allegations-are-co-ordinated-attack-against-him-3005962">以“毫无根据”为由否认了比安科的指控</a>，并于 2023 年 1 月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/games-of-thrones-actor-esme-bianco-and-marilyn-manson-reach-settlement-in-sexual-assault-lawsuit-3386310">与她达成和解</a>。</p><p> 2023 年 9 月，他还被一位名叫 Jane Doe 的人指控——不过，她的案件<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-reportedly-settles-sexual-assault-lawsuit-a-week-ahead-of-trial-3506325">在开庭前一周就得到了和解</a>。</p><p>去年 12 月的其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-sexual-assault-lawsuit-filed-by-former-assistant-revived-3558852">他的前助理阿什利·沃尔特斯 (Ashley Walters) 赢得了一项关键上诉，使她的案件得以恢复</a>，该案件最初于 2022 年被驳回。下个月，他将面临沃尔特斯在洛杉矶法院提起的诉讼。</p><p>与此同时，曼森<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-announces-first-tour-since-sexual-abuse-allegations-3599063">将于八月和九月在北美举办一系列演出，</a>支持<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/five-finger-death-punch">五指死亡拳</a>。</p><p>即将在曼森即将举行的三场演出中为曼森开场的乐队“葬礼肖像”(The Funeral Portrait <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/band-opening-for-marilyn-manson-respond-to-backlash-before-deleting-comments-3753551">) 也因演出而遭到强烈反对。他们在删除对此事的评论之前做出了回应。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-seems-to-have-signed-new-record-deal-with-nuclear-blast-amidst-abuse-allegations-3756751">玛丽莲·曼森 (Marilyn Manson) 似乎在虐待指控中与 Nuclear Blast 签署了新的唱片协议，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
